---
const personalImageAlt = "Sebastian Gutierrez Guayacundo";
import DiscordIcon from "@/components/icons/Discord.astro";
import GitHubIcon from "@/components/icons/GitHub.astro";
import GmailIcon from "@/components/icons/Gmail.astro";
import InstagramIcon from "@/components/icons/Instagram.astro";
import LinkedInIcon from "@/components/icons/LinkedIn.astro";
import Twitter from "@/components/icons/Twitter.astro";
import YoutubeIcon from "@/components/icons/Youtube.astro";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden mt-10 lg:mt-0 bg-[#FAFAFA]">
    <div class="mx-64 w-full xl:max-w-full">
        <div
            class="relative z-10 pb-8 sm:pb-16 md:pb-20 lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-2xl lg:pb-28 xl:pb-32"
        >
            <main class="mx-auto px-4 pt-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 sm:pt-12 md:pt-20">
                <h1
                    class="font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 text-4xl sm:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
                >
                    Soy Sebastian
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
                >
                    Acelero el <strong class="font-semibold text-[#D32F2F]"
                        >crecimiento de proyectos</strong
                    > mediante soluciones tecnológicas avanzadas, análisis de datos,
                    optimización y automatización de procesos.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 sm:mt-5 sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
                >
                    Me considero un <strong
                        class="font-semibold text-[#D32F2F]">apasionado</strong
                    > por la tecnología, los números, los datos y por emprender.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="mt-3 text-gray-600 xl:max-w-xl sm:mt-5 text-base sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0"
                >
                    ¡Si compartes mis intereses o necesitas apoyo en tu
                    proyecto, sigue explorando para descubrir cómo podemos <strong
                        class="font-semibold text-[#D32F2F]"
                        >crecer juntos</strong
                    >!
                </p>

                <nav class="flex gap-8 mt-4 lg:mt-6 flex-wrap">
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/soyy_sebas/">
                        <InstagramIcon
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://linktr.ee/soyysebas">
                        <YoutubeIcon
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/SoyySebas">
                        <Twitter
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastian-gutierrez-guayacundo-43b165288"
                    >
                        <LinkedInIcon
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/Soy-Sebas">
                        <GitHubIcon
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/1140012750874099772">
                        <DiscordIcon
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                    <a href="mailto:sggbusiness.co@gmail.com">
                        <GmailIcon
                            class="size-7 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                        />
                    </a>
                </nav>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div
        class="bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-500 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2 h-auto hidden lg:block"
    >
        <img
            class="h-56 w-full object-cover lg:h-full"
            src="./photos/HeroIm.jpeg"
            alt={personalImageAlt}
        />
    </div>
</section>
